{
    "text": "Zakynthos island, home to some of the most ethereal beaches? \ud83c\udf0a\ud83c\udfdd   Zakynthos is one of the most popular Greek islands \ud83c\uddec\ud83c\uddf7 with stunning landscapes, dreamy beaches with white sand and crystal clear turquoise waters are the main reasons why this island is so famous. \ud83d\udc99   Did you know? \ud83d\ude2f Zakynthos island and Rhodes island share top place as having the longest annual sun exposure in Greece. \u2600  Follow @travelmosa Follow @travelmosa Follow @travelmosa \ud83d\udcf8: @jess.wandering  \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 #Seascape #zakynthos #zakynthosisland  #clearsea #explorepage #explore #greece #greekisland",
